OL,3,CFamily of late Leicester City chairman
OL,4,Csue helicopter manufacturer for #2.1bn
OL,6,FHis family are seeking #2.15bn in
OL,7,Fcompensation for loss of earnings as a
OL,8,Fresult of the Thai billionaire's
OL,9,Fdeath, the pain he experienced before
OL,10,Fhe died, and funeral expenses, the
OL,11,FStewarts law firm said.
OL,13,FIt said Air Accident Investigation
OL,14,FBranch (AAIB) report said "serious
OL,15,Fconcerns" had been raised about the
OL,16,Faircraft's safety, according to
OL,17,FStewarts.
