OL,3,CFamily of late Leicester City chairman
OL,4,Csue helicopter manufacturer for #2.1bn
OL,6,FIt said the family launched High Court
OL,7,Faction on Friday, and added: "The
OL,8,Freport found the crash was caused by
OL,9,Fthe seizure of a key component located
OL,10,Fin the tail rotor, which Leonardo had
OL,11,Fidentified in the design phase as
OL,12,Fbeing critical, and its failure
OL,13,Fcatastrophic.
OL,15,F"This failure prompted a sequence of
OL,16,Ffurther failures which drove the
OL,17,Fhelicopter into an uncontrollable and
OL,18,Faccelerating spin until it crashed and
OL,19,Ferupted into flames."
