OL,3,CFamily of late Leicester City chairman
OL,4,Csue helicopter manufacturer for #2.1bn
OL,6,FThe claim also alleges the
OL,7,Fmanufacturer failed to warn customers
OL,8,For regulators about the risk.
OL,10,FThe AAIB report concluded there was
OL,11,Fnothing the pilot could have done to
OL,12,Fprevent the crash.
OL,14,FThe legal team's statement said: "The
OL,15,Fclaim seeks compensation for the loss
OL,16,Fof earnings and other damages, valued
OL,17,Fat #2.15 billion, which were the
OL,18,Fresult of Khun Vichai's premature
OL,19,Fdeath."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/13
