OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F378A1736774956
OL,3,CFamily of late Leicester City chairman
OL,4,Csue helicopter manufacturer for #2.1bn
OL,6,F"At the time of the crash, King Power,
OL,7,Fwhich was founded by Khun Vichai, was
OL,8,Fearning revenue in excess of #2.5
OL,9,Fbillion per year and had a net profit
OL,10,Fwhich peaked at #237 million the year
OL,11,Fbefore his death."
OL,13,F"That success was driven by Khun
OL,14,FVichai's vision, drive, relationships,
OL,15,Fentrepreneurism, ingenuity and
OL,16,Freputation. All of this was lost with
OL,17,Fhis death."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/13
