OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe helicopter crashed shortly after
OL,12,FCity's Premier League game against
OL,13,FWest Ham on Saturday 27 October. It
OL,14,Fcame down in a car park alongside the
OL,15,Fground shortly and moments after it
OL,16,Fhad taken off from the pitch.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/13
