OL,3,CFamily of late Leicester City chairman
OL,4,Csue helicopter manufacturer for #2.1bn
OL,6,FPolice and emergency services rushed
OL,7,Fto the scene and made effort to rescue
OL,8,Fthe people trapped inside the
OL,9,Fhelicopter, which was by that point
OL,10,Fengulfed in flames.
OL,12,FKhun Aiyawatt Srivaddhanaprabha, Khun
OL,13,FVichai's son and successor as club
OL,14,Fchairman, said today: "My family feels
OL,15,Fthe loss of my father as much today as
OL,16,Fwe ever have done."
OL,18,F"That my own children, and their
OL,19,Fcousins will never know their
OL,20,Fgrandfather compounds our suffering."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/13
