OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F378A1736774956
OL,3,CFamily of late Leicester City chairman
OL,4,Csue helicopter manufacturer for #2.1bn
OL,6,F"We have reflected on the conclusions
OL,7,Fof the AAIB report and thought
OL,8,Fcarefully about how we wished to
OL,9,Fproceed."
OL,11,F"My father trusted Leonardo when he
OL,12,Fbought that helicopter, but the
OL,13,Fconclusions of the report into his
OL,14,Fdeath show that his trust was fatally
OL,15,Fmisplaced. I hold them wholly
OL,16,Fresponsible for his death."
OL,18,FThe family is represented by aviation
OL,19,Flaw firm, Stewarts.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
