OL,3,CFamily of late Leicester City chairman
OL,4,Csue helicopter manufacturer for #2.1bn
OL,6,FPeter Neenan, a partner at Stewarts
OL,7,Fwho is representing the family, said:
OL,8,F"The foundation of the claim brought
OL,9,Fagainst Leonardo is the independent
OL,10,FAAIB report released in September
OL,11,F2023."
OL,13,F"Considering the purview of the AAIB's
OL,14,Fmission is to report on safety and not
OL,15,Fto blame, the report was as damning a
OL,16,Freport as I have ever read.
OL,18,FHe added: "The claim takes that safety-
OL,19,Fdriven analysis to its eventual
OL,20,Fimplication in allegations" of
OL,21,F"negligence".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/13
