OL,3,CFamily of late Leicester City chairman
OL,4,Csue helicopter manufacturer for #2.1bn
OL,6,F"Leonardo's customers include national
OL,7,Fmilitaries, air ambulances and other
OL,8,Ffirst responders across the globe.
OL,10,F"It is critical that all operators of
OL,11,Fthese helicopters have faith and
OL,12,Fconfidence in the machines," said Mr
OL,13,FNeenan.
OL,15,FAn inquest into the helicopter crash
OL,16,Fis set to start in Leicester on Monday.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/13
