OL,6,FThe helicopter company Leonardo also
OL,7,Fgave a statement: "Leonardo has the
OL,8,Fdeepest sympathy for those who lost
OL,9,Ftheir lives in the accident, all of
OL,10,Fthem clearly loved by their families,
OL,11,Ffriends and communities.
OL,13,F"Their deaths were an unquestionable
OL,14,Ftragedy."
OL,16,F"Leonardo is aware of the claim which
OL,17,Fhas been issued by Vichai
OL,18,FSrivaddhanaprabha's family in the
OL,19,FEnglish High Court and is considering
OL,20,Fthis with its legal advisers and
OL,21,Finsurers."
