OL,6,F"Leonardo intends to defend this
OL,7,Fclaim."
OL,9,F"Leonardo notes that the AAIB Final
OL,10,FReport, released in September 2023,
OL,11,Fhas not directed any Recommended
OL,12,FActions to Leonardo."
OL,14,F"The AAIB report concluded that
OL,15,FLeonardo complied with all regulatory
OL,16,Frequirements in both the design and
OL,17,Fmanufacture of the AW169."
